downloadDescription: The IntelliTrace collector is a standalone tool that you can use to collect IntelliTrace data from apps that are running in production environments.
detailsSection: The IntelliTrace collector is a standalone tool that you can use to collect IntelliTrace data from apps that are running in production environments. To analyze the data that's collected, you must use Visual Studio Ultimate 2012 or Visual Studio Ultimate 2013 or Visual Studio Enterprise 2015.
systemRequirementsSection:
Hardware Requirements:
  • 1.6 GHz or faster processor
  • 1 GB of RAM (1.5 GB if running on a virtual machine)
  • 5 MB of available hard disk space
  • 5400 RPM hard disk drive
  • DirectX 9-capable video card running at 1024 x 768 or higher display resolution


Supported Visual Studio versions
  • Visual Studio 2012 Ultimate
  • Visual Studio 2013 Ultimate
  • Visual Studio 2015 Enterprise
installInstructionSection:
• On this page, choose the Download button.
    • To install the software now, choose the Run button.
    • To install the software later, choose the Save button
  • When the installation is complete, the IntelliTrace.cab file is located in the selected installation location. Follow these instructions to expand and use the utilities in the .cab file.
